PN,30607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1777579557
OL,3,CRecommended use of some nasal sprays
OL,4,Climited to five days, regulator
OL,5,Cannounces
OL,7,F"These nasal sprays are safe and
OL,8,Feffective treatments when used as
OL,9,Fdirected. It is important to always
OL,10,Fread the Patient Information Leaflet
OL,11,Fthat comes with your medicine and
OL,12,Finformation on the outer packaging."
OL,14,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,15,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,16,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,17,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1777579557
OL,3,CRecommended use of some nasal sprays
OL,4,Climited to five days, regulator
OL,5,Cannounces
OL,7,FThe Royal College of Pharmacy said it
OL,8,Fwelcomed the move, after having
OL,9,Fpreviously called for a change in
OL,10,Flabelling.
OL,12,FProfessor Amira Guirguis, chief
OL,13,Fscientist at the organisation, said:
OL,14,F"We support clearer product
OL,15,Finformation and improved packaging,
OL,16,Falongside consistent public messaging,
OL,17,Fto improve awareness that these
OL,18,Fproducts are for short-term use only
OL,19,Fand to avoid preventable harm.
OL,26,@vD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
