PN,30609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1777579557
OL,3,CRecommended use of some nasal sprays
OL,4,Climited to five days, regulator
OL,5,Cannounces
OL,7,F"Pharmacists play a key role in
OL,8,Fsupporting patients to use them safely
OL,9,Fand advising on safer alternatives
OL,10,Fwhere appropriate."
OL,12,FSuspected side effects associated with
OL,13,Fxylometazoline and oxymetazoline can
OL,14,Fbe reported to the MHRA through its
OL,15,FYellow Card scheme.
OL,17,FIf you have any concerns, contact your
OL,18,FGP.
